line_1: From seven-mouth'd Nilus, to the frozen Don,
line_2: How art thou tumbled from thine Alpine throne!

line_1: From seven-mouth'd Nilus, to the frozen Don,
line_2: Thou sittedst erst unequall'd and alone,

line_1: From seven-mouth'd Nilus, to the frozen Don,
line_2: And madedst through the world thy greatness known;
